{
  "stem": "15943.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So every time we would stay in the morning and at night-- again, the same thing was repeated-- we never knew if we're going to get before bedtime whatever we're supposed to get, a bowl of soup or a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She might decide she doesn't want to give it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So the-- that, that was her games.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Whatever she wanted to do that day or that moment, then that's how she decided for punishment.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "When we came to the factory, the first speech was also-- it was a factory that was making parts to airplanes-- electric drills.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the foreman spoke to us in German.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We understood German.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he said, if somebody makes a mistake, it's sabotage.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And you're responsible for one another.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We were always responsible for one another and getting punished for it, for talking to the foreman, which we weren't supposed to.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[SIGHS] They always found reasons.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Whatever you did that-- one person, according to them, did something wrong.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We were always punished.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So there were many times that what little food we were supposed to get was taken away.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Lotte, Lotte.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know any last names of them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah, Lotte.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were a lot of Lottes there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were several guards that were called Lotte.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I guess Gerte and Lotte were popular German names.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So no, we didn't-- of course, we didn't know any, any last names.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "To them, we didn't have any names.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We're just parasites.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the, the guards were German girls that grew up under Nazi Germany.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And what they knew about Jews, they learned from Nazi literature.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "To them, we were just parasites.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
